OL,3,CSalford City Council to take full
OL,4,Cownership of Salford Community Stadium
OL,6,FThe council, which already controls
OL,7,F50% of the site, is discussing a deal
OL,8,Fto buy the remaining half of the
OL,9,Fground which is owned by property
OL,10,Fcompany Peel.JIt will see the council
OL,11,Ftake full control over the stadium and
OL,12,Fsurrounding land, including car
OL,13,Fparking areas and training pitches.
OL,14,FEmpty land around the stadium is
OL,15,Fexpected to be sold for regeneration
OL,16,Fprojects to finance the agreement once
OL,17,Fcomplete.JThe future of was left in
OL,18,Fdoubt last year until a 12-month
OL,19,Fextension on the stadium lease was
OL,20,Fagreed with the ground's co-owners.
