OL,3,CSalford City Council to take full
OL,4,Cownership of Salford Community Stadium
OL,6,FSalford City Mayor Paul Dennett said:
OL,7,F"I am delighted that we are nearing
OL,8,Fconclusion of months of painstaking
OL,9,Fdiscussions.
OL,11,F"We'll be able to recommit to deliver
OL,12,Fthe initial vision of a community
OL,13,Fstadium for the city and its people.
OL,15,F"The future will be grounded in a new
OL,16,Fsports and leisure and strategy, with
OL,17,Flinks to activity, culture and health
OL,18,Fand wellbeing and fair access and
OL,19,Fopportunities.
