OL,6,F"These benefits will go far beyond
OL,7,Factivities on the pitch, with full
OL,8,Fdevelopment of the site creating an
OL,9,Fanticipated 790 new jobs, delivering
OL,10,F#28million worth of social value and
OL,11,Fattracting #65 million of private
OL,12,Fsector investment."
OL,14,FManaging Director of , Paul King said:
OL,15,F"This is certainly a big step in the
OL,16,Fright direction, and hopefully this
OL,17,Fcan now lead to a swiftly agreed deal.
OL,19,F"I can't understate how important the
OL,20,Fconclusion of the deal is for the club.
