OL,3,CSalford City Council to take full
OL,4,Cownership of Salford Community Stadium
OL,6,FSale Sharks Chief Executive Paul Smith
OL,7,Fsaid: "The future of the Salford
OL,8,FCommunity Stadium has been a
OL,9,Fprotracted saga that has caused a huge
OL,10,Famount of uncertainty both within the
OL,11,Fclub and among our fanbase for too
OL,12,Flong.J"While there is still work to
OL,13,Fdo, this announcement hopefully begins
OL,14,Fto draw a line under the questions
OL,15,Faround stadium ownership and allows us
OL,16,Fall to start working together to
OL,17,Fcreate a real hub , across both codes,
OL,18,Fin the north."JThe council's deal to
OL,19,Fbuy the stadium and surrounding land
OL,20,Fis expected to cost around #2m in
OL,21,Ftotal.JThe deal will also see the
OL,22,Fcouncil taking on the #38m of debt
OL,23,Fowed by the stadium company, according
OL,24,Fto Salford's mayor.
